WEBVTT

1
00:00:00.500 --> 00:00:01.146
What are you making?

2
00:00:02.487 --> 00:00:03.680
Ratatouille. Is that OK?

3
00:00:05.127 --> 00:00:08.520
Don't, Lara. Give me my phone. Give it.

4
00:00:08.973 --> 00:00:09.927
No. Who is this?

5
00:00:10.695 --> 00:00:13.568
I don't know. I don't read your messages, it's none of your business.

6
00:00:14.564 --> 00:00:16.682
- Do you? - No, I don't.

7
00:00:16.715 --> 00:00:18.516
- No? Who is it? - Give me my phone.

8
00:00:19.711 --> 00:00:22.704
I can't see who it is. Give me my phone so I can see.

9
00:00:24.494 --> 00:00:25.281
Give it to me.

10
00:00:28.049 --> 00:00:29.648
I've seen who it is. Give it back.

11
00:00:40.082 --> 00:00:41.948
It's Christine. It's...

12
00:00:43.275 --> 00:00:44.042
It's Christine.

13
00:00:44.824 --> 00:00:48.181
- Yes, thanks. - She's a new friend of mine.

14
00:00:50.306 --> 00:00:52.385
And no, before you ask.

15
00:00:52.938 --> 00:00:54.232
She's not my girlfriend.

16
00:00:55.860 --> 00:00:58.073
- I wasn't going to ask. - Yeah, right.

17
00:00:59.588 --> 00:01:00.861
Not yet, anyway.

18
00:01:03.745 --> 00:01:07.257
- But is it going well? - I don't know where it's going.

19
00:01:08.053 --> 00:01:10.693
I don't even know if it's going anywhere, but...

20
00:01:12.919 --> 00:01:13.486
We'll see.

